    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out consistent with ASME V&V 40 Table 1 guidance for MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. Decision recorded under ProfileMinimal; no structured Context of Use object is present in this package.",
